Say '''Candoni''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Negros Occidental]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 21,336 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 191.7 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumapat ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6110.	
															
